metadata.name: One Snowy Night in Times Sq.
metadata.description:
For most- treading through Times Sq. during a blizzard becomes a seemingly insurmountable task - it is not fun. But for the photographers, Times Sq. becomes a playground of beautiful neon lights only made brighter and more vibrant by the opaque blanket of snow that covers the city and the sky.  

one snowy night in times square... 

minted: 12/19/21
